summary: Working on webtoon comic and trying many times to write a good description. Man I suck at this. I'll keep y'all updated on it....
body:
Working on webtoon comic and trying many times to write a good description. Man I suck at this. I’ll keep y'all updated on it.

This comic will include the last remaining Minecraft players(setosorcerer, jeromeasf, captainsparklez and antvenom) and these dudes are protected by the twitch characters(ClassicPsy and Jerome’s girlfriend). I’m excited to make this as a fun side comic while I wait for my writer to get back to me on my Mika Nyland comic project idea(“it’ll be huge”). For now everything is work in progress drafts. Enjoy this for now
